	<data name="Privacy_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>Privacy Policy</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_Updated" xml:space="preserve"><value>Last updated: March 2025</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_Intro" xml:space="preserve"><value>Lawllit respects your privacy. This Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect the personal data of lawllit.finance users, in accordance with the Brazilian General Data Protection Law (Lei nº 13.709/2018).</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>1. Data we collect</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Intro" xml:space="preserve"><value>We collect only the data necessary to provide the service:</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Li1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Name and email address, provided at registration</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Li2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Google account identifier, when registration is done via Google</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Li3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Financial transactions you record: description, amount, type, date, and recurrence</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Li4" xml:space="preserve"><value>Categories you create to organize your transactions</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Li5" xml:space="preserve"><value>Personalization preferences: visual theme, font size, language, and currency</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S1_Li6" xml:space="preserve"><value>Session token, required to keep you authenticated for up to 7 days</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S2_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>2. How we use your data</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S2_Li1" xml:space="preserve"><value>To create and manage your account</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S2_Li2" xml:space="preserve"><value>To display your personalized financial dashboard</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S2_Li3" xml:space="preserve"><value>To send transactional emails: email confirmation and password reset</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S2_Li4" xml:space="preserve"><value>To apply your interface preferences on each visit</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S3_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>3. Data sharing</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S3_Body1" xml:space="preserve"><value>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for commercial or advertising purposes.</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S3_Body2" xml:space="preserve"><value>lawllit.finance fetches exchange rate data through the public API economia.awesomeapi.com.br. This request is made server-side and does not include any of your personal data.</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S4_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>4. Data retention</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S4_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>Your data is retained while your account is active. After account deletion, your data is removed from our systems within 30 days.</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S5_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>5. Your rights (LGPD)</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S5_Body_Pre" xml:space="preserve"><value>You have the right to access, correct, and delete your personal data at any time. Deletion can be done directly in the Profile section of lawllit.finance. For other privacy-related requests, contact us at</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S6_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>6. Security</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S6_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>Passwords are stored encrypted and never in plain text. We use anti-forgery tokens on all forms, industry-standard security headers, and rate limiting on authentication endpoints to protect your account.</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S7_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>7. Changes to this Policy</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S7_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>Any updates will be published on this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of the service after changes implies acceptance of the new version.</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S8_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>8. Contact</value></data>
	<data name="Privacy_S8_Body_Pre" xml:space="preserve"><value>For questions about this Policy, contact us at</value></data>

