	<data name="Terms_S1_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>By creating an account on lawllit.finance, you declare that you have read, understood, and agree to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree with any of the terms described here, do not use the service.</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S2_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>2. The Service</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S2_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>lawllit.finance is a personal finance management application that allows you to record income and expenses, organize categories, track your balance, and view real-time exchange rates. The service is intended for individuals for personal use.</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S3_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>3. Registration and Account Responsibility</value></data>
