	<data name="Terms_S3_Li4" xml:space="preserve"><value>Each person may maintain only one active account in the service</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S4_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>4. Acceptable Use</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S4_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>lawllit.finance must be used exclusively for personal and lawful purposes. Using the service for illegal or fraudulent activities, or activities that may compromise the security or functioning of the platform, is prohibited.</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S5_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>5. Your Financial Data</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S5_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>All financial data you record in lawllit.finance belongs to you. Lawllit does not access, analyze, or use your transactions for any purpose beyond displaying them in your own dashboard. You may delete your account and all associated data at any time in the Profile section.</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S6_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>6. Exchange Rates and Financial Disclaimer</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S6_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>Exchange rates displayed on lawllit.finance are for informational purposes only and are sourced from public APIs. They do not constitute a recommendation to buy, sell, or invest in any financial asset or currency. Lawllit is not responsible for any financial decisions made based on the information displayed in this service.</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S7_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>7. Service Availability</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S7_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>lawllit.finance is provided without guarantee of continuous availability. The service may be interrupted for maintenance, updates, or reasons beyond our control. We are not liable for any losses resulting from temporary unavailability.</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S8_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>8. Account Termination</value></data>
	<data name="Terms_S8_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>You may delete your account at any time directly in the Profile section of lawllit.finance. Lawllit reserves the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms of Use, with or without prior notice.</value></data>
