	<data name="Terms_S9_Body" xml:space="preserve"><value>The Lawllit brand, design, interface, and code of lawllit.finance are the property of Lawllit. The financial data you record is your property. No part of the service may be reproduced, distributed, or used commercially without express authorization.</value></data>
